{
  "id": "599e86ae330d690011242d2a",
  "title": "仮説は実験して検証しよう",
  "created": 1503561391,
  "updated": 1524203614,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "599e86ae330d690011242d2a",
      "text": "仮説は実験して検証しよう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503561391,
      "updated": 1503561391
    },
    {
      "id": "599e86afaff09e0000d53320",
      "text": "from [灘校土曜講座2014]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503561391,
      "updated": 1503571848
    },
    {
      "id": "599e86afaff09e0000d53321",
      "text": "[仮説]は[実験]して[検証]しよう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503561391,
      "updated": 1503561402
    },
    {
      "id": "599e86afaff09e0000d53322",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/cca4bbd3aeb032f6804e28376501bcfb]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503561391,
      "updated": 1503561391
    },
    {
      "id": "599e86afaff09e0000d53323",
      "text": "88",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503561391,
      "updated": 1524203277
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad97f0caff09e0000068ab4",
      "text": " [仮説]は[実験]して[検証]しよう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203277,
      "updated": 1524203333
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad97f14aff09e0000068ab6",
      "text": " 勉強していて“わかった\"と思うことがあるだろうけど問題を解いてみたら解けなかったりするわけですよ。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203286,
      "updated": 1524203298
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad97f22aff09e0000068ab8",
      "text": " “わかった\"は仮説であって、実験して検証しなければ本当にわかっているのかわからない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203298,
      "updated": 1524203302
    },
    {
      "id": "599e86afaff09e0000d53324",
      "text": "\t\t[「わかった」は仮説]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503561391,
      "updated": 1524203317
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad97f3baff09e0000068abb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203323,
      "updated": 1524203323
    },
    {
      "id": "599e86afaff09e0000d53325",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/97f22919bb81f592a5a61f5b64569735]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503561391,
      "updated": 1503561391
    },
    {
      "id": "599e86afaff09e0000d53326",
      "text": "89",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503561391,
      "updated": 1524203339
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad97f4aaff09e0000068abc",
      "text": " 計画を立てて行動をして、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203339,
      "updated": 1524203399
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad97f4daff09e0000068abd",
      "text": " 行動の結果を考察して、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203342,
      "updated": 1524203346
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad97f51aff09e0000068abe",
      "text": " 結果を修正して行く、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203346,
      "updated": 1524203348
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad97f53aff09e0000068abf",
      "text": " このサイクルを回して事業を進めていく",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203348,
      "updated": 1524203351
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad97f57aff09e0000068ac0",
      "text": " [PDCAサイクル] [計画]→[行動]→[結果の考察]→[計画の修正]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203351,
      "updated": 1524203396
    },
    {
      "id": "599e86afaff09e0000d53327",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503561391,
      "updated": 1503561391
    },
    {
      "id": "599e86afaff09e0000d53328",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/20480050f8a40efe614570570ac5ce6a]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503561391,
      "updated": 1503561391
    },
    {
      "id": "599e86afaff09e0000d53329",
      "text": "90",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503561391,
      "updated": 1524203402
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad97f89aff09e0000068ac1",
      "text": "\t科学研究も似ていて",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203402,
      "updated": 1524203405
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad97f8caff09e0000068ac2",
      "text": "  仮説を立てて",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203405,
      "updated": 1524203417
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad97f98aff09e0000068ac3",
      "text": "  実験をし",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203416,
      "updated": 1524203419
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad97f9aaff09e0000068ac4",
      "text": "  実験結果が期待通りか考察して",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203419,
      "updated": 1524203422
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad97f9daff09e0000068ac5",
      "text": "  期待と違う時がチャンス、仮説を修正していく",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203422,
      "updated": 1524203429
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad97fa4aff09e0000068ac6",
      "text": " [仮説]→[実験]→[結果の考察]→[仮説の修正]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203429,
      "updated": 1524203451
    },
    {
      "id": "599e86afaff09e0000d5332a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503561391,
      "updated": 1503561391
    },
    {
      "id": "599e86afaff09e0000d5332b",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/3e2cff398be6cbbf146725815e1bb2f3]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503561391,
      "updated": 1503561391
    },
    {
      "id": "599e86afaff09e0000d5332c",
      "text": "91",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503561391,
      "updated": 1524203502
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad97feeaff09e0000068acd",
      "text": " 勉強でも同じ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203502,
      "updated": 1524203502
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad97fc8aff09e0000068ac8",
      "text": "  理解は仮説",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203465,
      "updated": 1524203504
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad97fcdaff09e0000068ac9",
      "text": "  理解に基づいた行動をして",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203470,
      "updated": 1524203504
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad97fd0aff09e0000068aca",
      "text": "  うまくいくと思ったのにうまく行かない＝自分の理解と異なる結果が得られた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203472,
      "updated": 1524203504
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad97fdcaff09e0000068acb",
      "text": "  これが理解を修正するチャンス",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203485,
      "updated": 1524203507
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad97fe1aff09e0000068acc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203489,
      "updated": 1524203496
    },
    {
      "id": "599e86afaff09e0000d5332f",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/d5de43692420d2b49cbe95e67c927e48]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503561391,
      "updated": 1503561391
    },
    {
      "id": "599e86afaff09e0000d53330",
      "text": "92",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503561391,
      "updated": 1524203510
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad97ff6aff09e0000068ace",
      "text": " このサイクルを小さく回すことで素早く学ぶ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203510,
      "updated": 1524203514
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad97ff9aff09e0000068acf",
      "text": " 例えばプログラミングなら",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203514,
      "updated": 1524203529
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad98009aff09e0000068ad2",
      "text": "  いきなり何千行のプログラムを書いて動かしてみて「動かなかった!」では学びが遅い。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203529,
      "updated": 1524203529
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad97fffaff09e0000068ad0",
      "text": "  小さな、1行とか数行とかで実行を繰り返して学んでいくのが効率が良い。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203519,
      "updated": 1524203532
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad98004aff09e0000068ad1",
      "text": " ビジネスだったら「これを求めている顧客がいる」を検証するための最小限の製品を作ってリリースし、検証していく。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203524,
      "updated": 1524203547
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad9801aaff09e0000068ad4",
      "text": " Dropboxが最初にリリースした製品は何だったでしょう?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203547,
      "updated": 1524203551
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad9801eaff09e0000068ad5",
      "text": "  彼らは製品を作らなかった。解説動画を作って事前登録フォームを置いた。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203551,
      "updated": 1524203551
    },
    {
      "id": "599e86afaff09e0000d53331",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503561391,
      "updated": 1503561391
    },
    {
      "id": "599e86afaff09e0000d53332",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/cf875330c50e78787f56c370c68061af]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503561391,
      "updated": 1503561391
    },
    {
      "id": "599e86afaff09e0000d53333",
      "text": "93",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1503561391,
      "updated": 1524203567
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad9802eaff09e0000068ad6",
      "text": " 河内先生:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203567,
      "updated": 1524203573
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad98035aff09e0000068ad7",
      "text": " \t期末考査なしで入試一発勝負だったらヤバイよね。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203573,
      "updated": 1524203576
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad98038aff09e0000068ad8",
      "text": "  だからこまめに試験をする。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203576,
      "updated": 1524203580
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad9803baff09e0000068ad9",
      "text": "  最初の一歩を小さくする。サイクルを小さくする。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203580,
      "updated": 1524203603
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad98052aff09e0000068ada",
      "text": " その通り、ただし「うまくいくと思ったけど失敗した」が大事。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203603,
      "updated": 1524203607
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad98057aff09e0000068adb",
      "text": "  失敗が学びのチャンス。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203607,
      "updated": 1524203613
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad9805caff09e0000068adc",
      "text": "  小テストをしばしば出すのもそういうこと",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524203613,
      "updated": 1524203614
    }
  ]
}